{"id":65,"parent_id":48,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":65,"title":"Luke 17","subtitle":"","short_title":"Luke","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 17"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus speaks of offenses, forgiveness, and faith—Even the faithful are unprofitable servants—Ten lepers are healed—Jesus discourses on the Second Coming."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.1","order":"03.05.017.7924"},["b","1"],"Then said he unto the disciples, It is impossible but that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"offences"],"will come: but woe",["i","unto him,"],"through whom they come!"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.2","order":"03.05.017.7925"},["b","2"],"It were better for him that a millstone were hanged about his neck, and he cast into the sea, than that he should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"offend"],"one of these little ones."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.3","order":"03.05.017.7926"},["b","3"],"¶Take heed to yourselves: If thy brother",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"trespass"],"against thee, rebuke him; and if he repent,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"forgive"],"him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.4","order":"03.05.017.7927"},["b","4"],"And if he trespass against thee seven times in a day, and seven times in a day turn again to thee, saying, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"repent"],"; thou shalt forgive him."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.5","order":"03.05.017.7928"},["b","5"],"And the apostles said unto the Lord, Increase our faith."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.6","order":"03.05.017.7929"},["b","6"],"And the Lord said, If ye had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"faith"],"as a grain of mustard seed, ye might say unto this sycamine tree, Be thou plucked up by the root, and be thou planted in the sea; and it should obey you."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.7","order":"03.05.017.7930"},["b","7"],"But which of you, having a servant plowing or",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"feeding cattle"],", will say unto him",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"by and by"],", when he is come from the field, Go and sit down to meat?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.8","order":"03.05.017.7931"},["b","8"],"And will not rather say unto him, Make ready wherewith I may sup, and gird thyself, and serve me, till I have eaten and drunken; and afterward thou shalt eat and drink?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.9","order":"03.05.017.7932"},["b","9"],"Doth he thank that servant because he did the things that were commanded him? I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"trow"],"not."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.10","order":"03.05.017.7933"},["b","10"],"So likewise ye, when ye shall have done all those things which are commanded you, say, We are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"unprofitable"],"servants: we have done that which was our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"duty"],"to do."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.11","order":"03.05.017.7934"},["b","11"],"¶And it came to pass, as he went to Jerusalem, that he passed through the midst of Samaria and Galilee."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.12","order":"03.05.017.7935"},["b","12"],"And as he entered into a certain village, there met him ten men that were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"lepers"],", which stood afar off:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.13","order":"03.05.017.7936"},["b","13"],"And they lifted up",["i","their"],"voices, and said, Jesus, Master, have mercy on us."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.14","order":"03.05.017.7937"},["b","14"],"And when he saw",["i","them,"],"he said unto them, Go shew yourselves unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"priests"],". And it came to pass, that, as they went, they were cleansed."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.15","order":"03.05.017.7938"},["b","15"],"And one of them, when he saw that he was healed, turned back, and with a loud voice glorified God,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.16","order":"03.05.017.7939"},["b","16"],"And fell down on",["i","his"],"face at his feet, giving him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"thanks"],": and he was a Samaritan."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.17","order":"03.05.017.7940"},["b","17"],"And Jesus answering said, Were there not ten",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"cleansed"],"? but where",["i","are"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"nine"],"?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.18","order":"03.05.017.7941"},["b","18"],"There are not found that returned to give glory to God, save this stranger."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.19","order":"03.05.017.7942"},["b","19"],"And he said unto him, Arise, go thy way: thy faith hath made thee whole."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.20","order":"03.05.017.7943"},["b","20"],"¶And when he was demanded of the Pharisees, when the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"kingdom"],"of God should come, he answered them and said, The kingdom of God cometh not with observation:"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.21","order":"03.05.017.7944"},["b","21"],"Neither shall they say, Lo here! or, lo there! for, behold, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"kingdom"],"of God",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"is"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"within"],"you."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.22","order":"03.05.017.7945"},["b","22"],"And he said unto the disciples, The days will come, when ye shall desire to see one of the days of the Son of man, and ye shall not see",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.23","order":"03.05.017.7946"},["b","23"],"And they shall say to you, See here; or,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"see"],"there: go not after",["i","them,"],"nor follow",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.24","order":"03.05.017.7947"},["b","24"],"For as the lightning, that lighteneth out of the one",["i","part"],"under heaven, shineth unto the other",["i","part"],"under heaven; so shall also the Son of man be in his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"day"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.25","order":"03.05.017.7948"},["b","25"],"But first must he suffer many things, and be rejected of this generation."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.26","order":"03.05.017.7949"},["b","26"],"And as it was in the days of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Noe"],", so shall it be also in the days of the Son of man."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.27","order":"03.05.017.7950"},["b","27"],"They did eat, they drank, they married wives, they were given in marriage, until the day that Noe entered into the ark, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"flood"],"came, and destroyed them all."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.28","order":"03.05.017.7951"},["b","28"],"Likewise also as it was in the days of Lot; they did eat, they drank, they bought, they sold, they planted, they builded;"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.29","order":"03.05.017.7952"},["b","29"],"But the same day that Lot went out of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"Sodom"],"it rained fire and brimstone from heaven, and destroyed",["i","them"],"all."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.30","order":"03.05.017.7953"},["b","30"],"Even thus shall it be in the day when the Son of man is revealed."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.31","order":"03.05.017.7954"},["b","31"],"In that day, he which shall be upon the housetop, and his stuff in the house, let him not come down to take it away: and he that is in the field, let him likewise not return back."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.32","order":"03.05.017.7955"},["b","32"],"Remember",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"Lot’s"],"wife."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.33","order":"03.05.017.7956"},["b","33"],"Whosoever shall seek to save his life shall lose it; and whosoever shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"lose"],"his life shall preserve it."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.34","order":"03.05.017.7957"},["b","34"],"I tell you, in that night there shall be two",["i","men"],"in one bed; the one shall be taken, and the other shall be left."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.35","order":"03.05.017.7958"},["b","35"],"Two",["i","women"],"shall be grinding together; the one shall be taken, and the other left."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.36","order":"03.05.017.7959"},["b","36"],"Two",["i","men"],"shall be in the field; the one shall be taken, and the other left."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.37","order":"03.05.017.7960"},["b","37"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"And"],"they answered and said unto him, Where, Lord? And he said unto them, Wheresoever the body",["i","is,"],"thither will the eagles be gathered together."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.1a","order":"03.05.017.7961"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/offense"},"TG Offense"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.2a","order":"03.05.017.7963"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.3a","order":"03.05.017.7965"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.15.15-17"},"Matt. 18:15 (15–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.3b","order":"03.05.017.7967"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.4a","order":"03.05.017.7969"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.6a","order":"03.05.017.7971"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.13"},"Moses 7:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.7a","order":"03.05.017.7973"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"tending a flock."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.7b","order":"03.05.017.7975"},["b","7b"],["span.small","GR"],"immediately."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.9a","order":"03.05.017.7977"},["b","9a"],["span.small","GR"],"think."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.10a","order":"03.05.017.7979"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/3.12"},"Rom. 3:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.21.20-26"},"Mosiah 2:21 (20–26)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ingratitude"},"Ingratitude"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.10b","order":"03.05.017.7981"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/duty"},"TG Duty"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.12a","order":"03.05.017.7983"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leprosy"},"TG Leprosy"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.14a","order":"03.05.017.7985"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/13.49"},"Lev. 13:49"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.16a","order":"03.05.017.7987"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.17a","order":"03.05.017.7989"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purification"},"TG Purification"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.17b","order":"03.05.017.7991"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ingratitude"},"TG Ingratitude"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.20a","order":"03.05.017.7993"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"},"TG Kingdom of God, on Earth"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.21a","order":"03.05.017.7995"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/65.2"},"D&C 65:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.21b","order":"03.05.017.7997"},["b","21b"],["span.small","JST"],"Luke 17:21 …",["i","has already come unto"],"you."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.21c","order":"03.05.017.7999"},["b","21c"],"Many translations read “among” because the pronoun “you” is plural here in Greek."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.23a","order":"03.05.017.8001"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-christs"},"TG False Christs"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.24a","order":"03.05.017.8003"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.34"},"Luke 21:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/5.4"},"1 Thes. 5:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.26a","order":"03.05.017.8005"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-cleansing-of"},"TG Earth, Cleansing of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/flood"},"Flood"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.27a","order":"03.05.017.8007"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.37.36-38"},"Matt. 24:37 (36–38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.29a","order":"03.05.017.8009"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.24"},"Gen. 19:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.32a","order":"03.05.017.8011"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.26"},"Gen. 19:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.33a","order":"03.05.017.8013"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/17.37a","order":"03.05.017.8015"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-luke/17.36-40"},["span.small","JST"],"Luke 17:36–40 (Appendix)"],"."]]}
